## ğŸ§ª Video Upload Workflow

- **1080p setting** = 15 seconds max recording
- **720p setting** = 30 seconds max
- I use 720p so I can upload longer clips to GitHub

I record videos right inside GitHub and upload them directly. Just rename the file and it's good to go â€” plays perfectly on desktop and mobile browsers.

